premise_source_doc_sentence: She has since moved into film production and is a partner at the Los Angeles entertainment law firm Pryor Cashman , specializing in film finance ; Robson has helped produce films ranging from Nick Nolte 's Affliction to Sylvester Stallone 's Cliffhanger .

While continuing to work as a film critic from the 1950s on , including pursuing a vigorous debate on the nature of cinematic realism with Taihei Imamura , Iwasaki helped produce some of the independent films made by Tadashi Imai and Satsuo Yamamoto after many left-wingers were expelled from the major studios in the Red Purge .
